    <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock screensteps-wrapper--introduction screensteps-wrapper">
  <div id="text-content_902e0c15-a2dd-4508-89ab-71f63ac56d13" class="text-block-content">
    <p>You can mention a user in a discussion reply in Discussions Redesign.</p>
<p><strong>Notes: </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Mentioning users is not supported in anonymous discussions. </li>
<li>Mentioning users is related to a <a href="https://community.canvaslms.com/t5/Canvas-Resource-Documents/Canvas-Course-Role-Permissions/ta-p/387080" target="_blank">course role permission</a>. If you are not able to mention users, the required permission may not be enabled for your role.</li>
</ul>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_discussions" data-step-uuid="279a262b-d4c2-44dd-82e2-f6a13dad58f2">
    <h2 id="open_discussions" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Discussions</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/733/185/original/b3b10c70-d27b-4f75-9d3c-c8b1b8f4d458.png" srcset="" alt="Open Discussions " height="280" width="179">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_93e851dd-5e5c-4051-9ed2-5fd5c50a66f2" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Discussions </strong>link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_discussion_topic" data-step-uuid="e95da4bd-c85f-4914-aca8-de5f753ad5d0">
